        "class": "ital",
        "text": "to give ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(to restore, to repay to them the mischief they have done to others) by the hand of thy extraordinary providence, because the oppressed were destitute of all other succours. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "The poor committeth himself unto thee — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
